of Seattle and Maryknoll invite you to join us in this
program which offers Catholic ministers and educators
the knowledge, skills, and resources to better help your
communities share the journey and go forth as agents of
encounter and positive Christian change. Join us for our
<i>Going Forth in Joy! Missionary Discipleship Formation
Program</i>; a weekend of encounter, prayer, and formation
for living the Gospel within and beyond the walls of
your parish, school, or office. Saturday and Sunday,
March 3-4 from 9am-3pm each day, offered in English
and Spanish. <i>Information</i>, 
<a href="mailto:seattle@maryknoll.org?subject=Catechist Formation - Going Forth in Joy">Anna Johnson</a>, 206-322-8831.</p>
